---
title: Poké Shelf
layout: layouts/pokeBase.njk
customcss: "/assets/css/shrines/pokemon/physical.css"
permalink: /shrines/pokemon/physical/
---

<section class="shelf-hero">
  <img class="poke-hero-sticker poke-hero-sticker--top-right poke-hero-sticker--medium"
       src="/assets/imgs/pokemon/graphics/heart-sticker.png"
       alt=""
       aria-hidden="true">

  <img class="poke-hero-sticker poke-hero-sticker--bottom-left poke-hero-sticker--small"
       src="/assets/imgs/pokemon/graphics/pink-bow.png"
       alt=""
       aria-hidden="true">

  <p class="shelf-kicker">Welcome to my Poké shelf</p>
  <h1>Poké Shelf</h1>
  <p>
    My little Pokémon shelf: games, figures, cards, plushies, and tiny treasures.
    This page is for the real-life PokéMart finds that live outside the save file.
  </p>
</section>

{% if pokemonPhotos.physicalTotal %}
<section class="shelf-section physical-photo-section">
  <div class="shelf-section__heading">
    <p class="shelf-kicker">Shelf photos</p>
    <h2>PokéMart display</h2>
  </div>

  {% for category in pokemonPhotos.physical %}
    {% if category.images and category.images.length %}
      <section class="physical-photo-category">
        <div class="physical-photo-category__heading">
          <h3>{{ category.label }}</h3>
          <p>{{ category.note }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pokemon-photo-grid pokemon-photo-grid--shelf">
          {% for photo in category.images %}
            <figure class="pokemon-photo-card">
              <img src="{{ photo.url }}" alt="{{ photo.alt }}" loading="lazy">
              <figcaption>{{ photo.caption }}</figcaption>
            </figure>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </section>
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
</section>
{% endif %}

<section class="shelf-section">
  <div class="shelf-section__heading">
    <p class="shelf-kicker">PokéMart shelf</p>
    <h2>Cosy collection corners</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="shelf-grid">
    <article class="shelf-card">
      <span class="shelf-card__icon">🎮</span>
      <h3>Physical Games</h3>
      <p>Cartridges, cases, boxes, and the games that started the whole collection.</p>
      <small>DS, 3DS, Switch, GBA, and anything else that joins the shelf.</small>
    </article>

    <article class="shelf-card">
      <span class="shelf-card__icon">🧸</span>
      <h3>Figures & Plush</h3>
      <p>Cute display pieces, tiny desk friends, and Pokémon that deserve their own little spot.</p>
      <small>Figures, plushies, mascots, keychains, and display bits.</small>
    </article>

    <article class="shelf-card">
      <span class="shelf-card__icon">🃏</span>
      <h3>TCG Binder</h3>
      <p>Cards I love, pretty art, favourite Pokémon, and anything too cute to hide away.</p>
      <small>Favourite pulls, promos, binders, and special pages.</small>
    </article>

    <article class="shelf-card">
      <span class="shelf-card__icon">🎀</span>
      <h3>Misc Treasures</h3>
      <p>Everything else: stationery, charms, pins, stickers, packaging, and silly little finds.</p>
      <small>The “I simply had to keep it” category.</small>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="shelf-section shelf-section--inventory">
  <div class="shelf-section__heading">
    <p class="shelf-kicker">Shelf notes</p>
    <h2>Favourite shelf notes</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="inventory-list">
    <article class="inventory-item">
      <span class="inventory-item__tag">Games</span>
      <h3>Main series shelf</h3>
      <p>
        A place to list the physical Pokémon games I own, with notes for favourite saves,
        childhood copies, current playthroughs, and boxed/cart-only status.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="inventory-item">
      <span class="inventory-item__tag">Display</span>
      <h3>Cute figure corner</h3>
      <p>
        A cosy display area for figures, plushies, and Pokémon merch that fits the shrine vibe.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="inventory-item">
      <span class="inventory-item__tag">Binder</span>
      <h3>Favourite cards</h3>
      <p>
        Not a full card database — just favourite TCG art, special cards, and anything I want
        to remember or show off.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="shelf-note">
  <p>
    <strong>Collection note:</strong> this page is now styled like a cosy PokéMart shelf.
    Add photos, counts, and favourite items here as the collection grows.
  </p>
</section>
